        {
            "id": 6310958,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 花旗集團(C-US)大跌5%，報110.48美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>花旗集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:C:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/C\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">C-US</a>)截至台北時間15日00:55股價下跌5.82美元，報110.48美元，跌幅5%，成交量12,412,125（股），盤中最高價118.75美元、最低價110.48美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.61%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.07%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.66%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.76%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>花旗集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:C:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/C\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">C-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-3.92%</li> <li>近 1 月：+5.28%</li> <li>近 3 月：+22.48%</li> <li>近 6 月：+34.51%</li> <li>今年以來：-0.84%</li></ul></section></main>",
